config MESHTASTIC_TRACEROUTE
	bool "Meshtastic TraceRoute responder"
	default y
	help
	  Register a port handler for incoming TRACEROUTE_APP (port 70)
	  requests: reply with a RouteDiscovery so the app or the reference
	  client `meshtastic --traceroute` can map the path to this node. The
	  reply appends this node's receive SNR to the towards-route, mirroring
	  the reference firmware's destination behavior.

	  Responder only: this flood-router port does not insert itself into the
	  route of traces passing through it, and has no local trace initiator.
